snippet.title: Fallout: The Frontier - Release Trailer
snippet.description:
Available on Nexus at: https://www.nexusmods.com/newvegas/mods/68009
Available on Steam at: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1356060/The_Frontier/ WHEN RELEASED


Thank you to Filip Adamczewski (Winters) for editing the trailer.

Web links :- 
Visit the website at: https://www.falloutthefrontier.com
Follow all progress on our discord at: https://discord.gg/Ergn7hj


"Fallout: The Frontier is supported by Creator's Network, a community that supports creative productions. If you are a mod author in need of personnel or someone looking to help out on a mod being developed, join us at  https://discord.gg/Dr3vVqZ".
